    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rapid prototyping process similar to stereolithography, except solid ground curing cures one layer of UV-sensitive photopolymer at a time. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
